{"word":"ἐμβριμάομαι","slug":"ἐμβριμάομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐμβριμάομαι</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἐν'><el>ἐν</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:aorist tense'>aor.</a> <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>mid.</a> et <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a>, <i>to snort in</i>, of horses, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>of persons, <i>to be deeply moved</i>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a> <i>to admonish urgently, rebuke</i>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}